title: ROLA 59401 TX Hitch Mount 4-Bike Carrier with Tilt & Security
features: Carries 4 bikes, sturdy, dual-arm support offers extra stability
Anti-sway rollers reduce bike movement during travel
Tilts down (even with bikes loaded) for rear of vehicle access; Arms fold down when not in use
Integrated, retractable cable lock offers improved bike security
description: The TX Series 4-Bike Rack features Dual arm support for extra stability. Tilt function to access vehicle without unloading bikes. Anti-sway rollers reduce bike movement. Large mouth cradles fit most bike frames. Integrated, retractable cable lock for improved bike security. Folding arms offer compact storage when not in use. Fits 2” receivers. An optional telescope tube to enable level transportation of bicycles with a sloping crossbar. (ROLA 6145)
